org.jorlib.frameworks.columnGeneration.io

Class SimpleDebugger

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jorlib.frameworks.columnGeneration.io.SimpleDebugger
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    EventListener, BAPListener, CGListener, CHListener

    public class SimpleDebugger
extends Object
implements BAPListener, CGListener, CHListener
    Simple class which helps debugging Branch-and-Price and Column Generation implementations. The debugger logs events originating from the Branch-and-Price instance, Column Generation instance(s) and the CutHandler.
    Version:
    21-5-2015
    Author:
    Joris Kinable
